sec.p:
To determine the molar amount of oligoribonucleotide synthesis product by T7 and Arabidopsis primase, the radioactive [α-32P]-ATP substrate and the oligonucleotide RNAs were quantified with ImageQuant. The processed intensity was subjected to the following equation, previously derived by the Patel group (34):
